overview: Carrie (Scarlet Red), is the best babysitter in town; everyone wants her. Between school and the high demand of her being great at her job, she's been spreading herself very thin. So when the calls all come in for the same night, she enlists her friends and fellow classmates Evie (Jodi Taylor) and Parker (Ava Dalush) to help, but nothing can prepare her for the mess that follows.
title: Lesbian Babysitters 12
